reviewText:
Yes, I finally found the complete Ilsa set in one collection. And, at a great price! Kinda cheap-looking imports but they play very well on my US DVD player and are all in English. Highly recommended, unless you're a collector.

Includes...

Ilsa - She-Wolf of the SS
Ilsa - Wicked Warden
Ilsa - Harem Keeper of the Oil Sheiks
Ilsa - Tigress of Siberia
